          <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zürich</placeName> d<supplied>en</supplied> <date when="1878-05-29">29 <hi>Mai</hi> <lb xml:id="p2-l20"/>1878</date>.
                </p>
      </div>
